feat(api): PR B3-ii-b — /ai/chat + /ai/chat/stream + sseproxy + ai_usage persist

- sseproxy: custom streaming proxy (reader + collector + translator + single-writer loop with frames/heartbeat select) — replaces the original AC #1 httputil.ReverseProxy path per approved decision (race between tee + heartbeat injection was not resolvable under ReverseProxy without hijacking response writer).
