- Idempotency middleware: skip cache-write on text/event-stream content-type; SETNX collapse preserved (AC #4).
- Cost clamp against NUMERIC(10,6) overflow with WARN log (R4).
- Frame cap: 1 MiB per SSE frame + ErrFrameTooLarge (R2).
- Re-serialise layer: AI Service frames translated to openapi AIChatStreamEvent shape — spec-align follow-up as TD-055.
- sqlc queries: InsertAIMessage, ListAIConversationMessagesForContext (role in user|assistant, ASC, cap 40), TouchAIConversation.

